com.vmware.vcenter.vcha

Interface OperationsTypes

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Operations
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    OperationsStub

    public interface OperationsTypes
    The Operations interface provides methods to figure out the currently active operations and currently disabled operations in a vCenter High Availability (VCHA) cluster. This interface was added in vSphere API 6.7.1.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  OperationsTypes.Info
      The Info class contains information about which the VCHA operations cannot be invoked in the current state of the system and the list of currently active VCHA operations.
